name: The "Robot of Ravetopia" - Galactibles™ #15
description: HOLY RAVING ROBOTS!! Congratulations, you’ve discovered Galactible™ #15,  the “Robot of Ravetopia!” Collecting this little dance partner allows you to conjure a Rave at any moment! Just feed this little robot some candy and they’ll be grooving by your side as you travel the Galactiverse! They even come with custom beats that slap your face right off your head! Your Mana has been raised by +1,000,000 bits! Custom beat made by Pyramid Guy! Galactibles™ are one-of-a-kind and minted as 1-of-1. Only 99 will be made! New Galactibles™ drop every week (sorta) on twitter, so give us a follow @Galactibles! Certified authentic and original animations made by Pyramid Guy (IG: @pyramidguy), aka Kris Kanaly (TW: @kriskanaly). Galactibles™ ©2021 | galactibles.com
